source: src/tests.rs
expression: render_command_help(&refs)
---
Count matching elements

Usage: bl count [OPTIONS] <selector>

Arguments:
  <selector>  CSS selector to count matches for

Options:
      --headless  Hide browser window (visible by default)
  -v, --verbose   Enable debug logging
      --json      Output as JSON
  -h, --help      Print help

Examples:
  bl count "a"
  # Print number of links on the page

  bl count "li.item"
  # Count list items
